<p>Dave&#039;s back from Mexico where the power is definitely the same. Yep, certianly. Or is it? He and John talk that through. Mostly, though, the show focuses on you: your questions, your tips, your thoughts, and your answers! Learn how to &quot;right-size&quot; Finder columns, use the keyboard to navigate System Preferences, re-enable your Mac&#039;s startup chime, manage Photos backups, boot a new Mac from an old one, and more! Press play to learn at least five new things!Note: Shownotes are complete!.</p>
